{"tid":1983910,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《一拳超人》開拍荷李活真人版電影 《毒魔》班底任編劇","createTime":"2020-04-22T06:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:31:38.000Z","uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd918b8d77a03e2587fd6cc7f13ec2b6e85eb7a","tid":1983910,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"據美國 Variety 等外電報導，知名動漫作品《一拳超人》將由索尼影業推出真人版電影，同時並指出該作的製作優先權相當高，因此也不排除有成為電影新系列作的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n由 ONE 擔任原作、村田雄介負責作畫的漫畫作品《一拳超人》，描述就職過程中找不到出路的主角「埼玉」，遭遇到要奪走一位少年生命的螃蟹異變人後，回憶起年少年時「想要成為英雄」的想法，於是奮起戰鬥並救下了少年。重拾對於成為英雄的志向後，埼玉苦練了三年、以掉光所有頭髮為代價，化身成毫無弱點的超級英雄，只需一拳便能輕鬆地擊敗怪獸。之後他與弟子傑諾斯一起加入了英雄協會，開始了與眾多英雄對抗各種怪物的生活。作品曾在 2015 年及 2019 年推出了兩季的電視動畫。<br />\n <br />\n　　本次將推出的真人版電影，將由曾經手《猛毒》的史考特&middot;羅森堡（Scott Rosenberg）與傑夫&middot;皮克納（Jeff Pinkner）負責劇本，製作人則是同樣經手過《猛毒》以及《蜘蛛人》系列作的阿維&middot;阿拉德（Avi Arad）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200422/X4B36QRVUDXCKV3WRJWHFMP3FA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2FX4B36QRVUDXCKV3WRJWHFMP3FA%2F&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8pq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6fcf35ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2FX4B36QRVUDXCKV3WRJWHFMP3FA%2F&h=c614d3d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200422/X4B36QRVUDXCKV3WRJWHFMP3FA/</a><br />\n<br />\n搵the rock<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcc4277e80ff14328cf6ecfe81bb547d10e8897","tid":1983910,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"大J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914bfb51113117f5f306e5f0e5971729092501d2","tid":1983910,"uid":40493,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"鬼佬做好怪喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"